      "timestep_posted": 13
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I am so excited to show you this absolute gem. Honestly, it\u2019s in such incredible shape that you\u2019d think it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve babied this car from day one\u2014it\u2019s spotless inside and out, drives like an absolute dream, and has been kept in pristine condition. If you're looking for a ride that feels brand new without the sticker shock, this is the one for you. Come take a look and fall in love!",
      "price": 46500.0,
