    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Available for acquisition is a pristine 2004 BMW M3 (E46) Coupe, a definitive example of Bavarian engineering. This vehicle is powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine, featuring individual throttle bodies and an 8,000 RPM redline. It is paired with a desirable Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox and a limited-slip M Differential Lock. This specimen is mechanically flawless: the vulnerable rear subframe has been professionally reinforced with plates, and both the rod bearings and dual-VANOS system have been serviced proactively with documented receipts. The chassis retains its factory-spec rigidity, utilizing refreshed bushings and Sachs dampers to preserve the original handling dynamics. Finished in Titanium Silver over Black Nappa leather, the aesthetic condition is commensurate with its mechanical excellence, showing no signs of bolster wear or paint degradation. A comprehensive service ledger is included, detailing a life of fastidious maintenance.",
      "price": 48500.0,
